product.name: 48 Port RJ45 Cat6 Patch Panel, 19 Inch, Black, Easy Install & Repair, Gold Plated Keystone, Rack Mountable
product.description:
With RJ45 Cat6 feed through coupler patch panel, clean up rack in 10 minutes.
48 port 2U keystone patch panel with Cat 6 inline coupler jacks is ideal for pre-terminated cat6 network cable installations.
Hours of time could be saved with 48 port patch panel cat6 pass through without any punching down.
Just plug Cat6 cables into the 48 RJ45 coupler jacks on both sides of the ethernet panel.
Unique features RJ45 plugs on both sides of the network patch panel.
Feed-through coupler keystone panel provide easy cable management bar.
Patch cat6 is perfect for both voice and data transmission.
Rj45 patch panel is equipped with gold plated inline keystone jacks which provide 10 Gigabit speed transmission performance.
The modular patch panel provides a quick and easy network installation.
Just plug Cat6 cables into the 48 RJ45 coupler jacks on both sides of the cat 6 patch panel.
cat6 gigabit connections for fast transmission.
48 CAT6 female-to-female RJ45 ports in 2U cat 6 patch panel.
No punchdown needed.
Gold plated contacts.
RJ45 coupler jacks on both side.
10Gigabit Ethernet applications.
Backwards compatible with CAT5e, and CAT5.
Removable rear cable management bar keeps cables neat and tidy.
Fit 19 inch rack or cabinet.
Mounting hardware and cable ties included.
Pass through Coupler Panels offer Category 6 system performance.
2u patch panel offer the perfect solution when a panel mounted high performance and high density plug-to-plug connection is required.
Keystone panel is suitable for patching cables terminated with RJ45 plugs.
Network patch panel cat 6 is a lower cost CAT6 utp panel with cable management bar.
48 ports RJ45 female cat6 coupler
RJ45 to RJ45 straight through
Dimensions (WxHxD) 482.6 x 87.2 x 91.5 mm
Weight 1.4kg
product.bullet_points:
• Easy Install: The pass through patch panel have female RJ45 ports on both side. No 110 punchdown termination is required for through coupler patch panel. This Ethernet patch panel provide a positive click for both side of each the ports.
• Easy Repair: The inline keystone patch panel can be easily repaired via just replace coupler keystone if the port don't work. Patch panel cat6 keeps the patch cable clean at the back of panel with the help of detachable cable management bar.
• Save Time: Hours of time could be saved with 48 port patch panel cat6 pass through without any punching down. Just plug Cat6 cables into the 48 RJ45 coupler jacks on both sides of the ethernet panel.
• Rack Mountable: The 2 U rack mount patch panel can be mounted in standard 19 inch network cabinet or rack. Secure the cables that plug into the back of rj45 jack panel by use of zip ties.
• Gold Plated Keystone: Rj45 patch panel is equipped with gold plated inline keystone jacks which provide 10 Gigabit speed transmission performance. Meets or exceeds Cat6 specifications. The keystone of coupler patch panel are removable if necessary for replacement or upgrade.
